were getting on with your plans.

00:13:13.780 --> 00:13:15.180
We would be delighted

00:13:15.180 --> 00:13:16.840
to host your son's
100th day celebration.

00:13:20.500 --> 00:13:22.340
Oh, you're hosting it
at Manjianghong Hotel?

00:13:24.540 --> 00:13:25.140
That's okay.

00:13:25.140 --> 00:13:26.820
I hope we have the chance to serve you

00:13:26.820 --> 00:13:28.180
in the future.

00:13:29.460 --> 00:13:31.340
May your baby grow strong and healthy.

00:13:31.980 --> 00:13:32.700
Okay.

00:13:33.100 --> 00:13:33.540
Goodbye.

00:13:39.380 --> 00:13:41.540
My mother made this beef sauce for you.

00:13:41.580 --> 00:13:42.980
It contains black wolf berries.

00:13:42.980 --> 00:13:44.100
Oh yeah, there's this too.

00:13:44.420 --> 00:13:45.700
And this paper bag as well.

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:46.760
It's dried bamboo shoots.

00:13:46.780 --> 00:13:48.540
Cook them with roasted pork,
and you'll be in for a treat.

00:13:48.540 --> 00:13:50.100
How can I finish them all?

00:13:50.100 --> 00:13:50.740
You can do it.

00:13:50.740 --> 00:13:51.740
Please help me thank...

00:13:52.220 --> 00:13:53.450
Thank your mother on my behalf.

00:13:54.460 --> 00:13:55.820
How is she doing?

00:13:55.820 --> 00:13:57.300
She's doing great.

00:13:57.540 --> 00:13:58.620
You may not know,

00:13:58.740 --> 00:14:00.700
but she's busy every day.

00:14:00.700 --> 00:14:02.380
She prepares three sets of everything.

00:14:02.380 --> 00:14:04.220
She's energetic way beyond her age.

00:14:04.340 --> 00:14:05.540
If we were in the ancient era,

00:14:05.540 --> 00:14:08.120
I suppose she could've joined
the military on Xu Zhidong's behalf.

00:14:12.020 --> 00:14:12.620
So,

00:14:13.340 --> 00:14:15.700
regarding my husband's selection,

00:14:16.080 --> 00:14:17.950
have you received any news
from your father-in-law?

00:14:18.100 --> 00:14:18.780
Not yet.

00:14:21.340 --> 00:14:23.500
What about this? I'll head back
and ask him about it.

00:14:24.980 --> 00:14:25.660
Mingzhu,

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:29.140
I know it's difficult for you
to ask for a favor there.

00:14:29.540 --> 00:14:30.940
I must've troubled you.

00:14:30.940 --> 00:14:31.820
I'm so sorry about this.

00:14:31.820 --> 00:14:32.660
It's fine.

00:14:32.940 --> 00:14:34.700
I only told my father-in-law about it.

00:14:34.700 --> 00:14:35.940
My mother-in-law has no idea.

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.420
I'm glad that it's not troubling you.

00:14:37.420 --> 00:14:38.060
Not at all.

00:14:38.980 --> 00:14:40.780
If Zhang Hao is promoted,

00:14:40.780 --> 00:14:42.580
he'll make an extra 10k or 20k per year.

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:45.920
You'll make the same amount
if you just publish a few more posts.

00:14:46.060 --> 00:14:47.340
My dear sister,

00:14:48.980 --> 00:14:51.340
you have no idea
how difficult it is to make money now.

00:14:51.620 --> 00:14:53.820
Official accounts
are popping up everywhere.

00:14:53.820 --> 00:14:55.260
Whenever there's a hot piece of news,

00:14:55.460 --> 00:14:57.420
people will write about it
from every angle.

00:14:57.420 --> 00:14:59.620
It's truly difficult for me
to gain attention.

00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:03.020
If your posts don't get many clicks,
they won't generate ad revenues.

00:15:03.020 --> 00:15:04.580
Without ads,
there's no way to make money.

00:15:04.580 --> 00:15:06.740
If there's no money,
I have to pay for it with my own.

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:08.340
I have to pay the office rent,

00:15:08.340 --> 00:15:09.900
utility bills, management fees...

00:15:10.340 --> 00:15:12.220
Oh yeah, and the wage of
my personal assistant.

00:15:12.220 --> 00:15:13.580
I have to pay all of that.

00:15:14.300 --> 00:15:16.100
Whenever I think about these bills,

00:15:16.220 --> 00:15:17.660
I can't sleep at night.

00:15:17.820 --> 00:15:19.820
It makes my hair fall out in clumps.

00:15:19.820 --> 00:15:20.460
Is that so?

00:15:21.340 --> 00:15:22.980
I suppose you have a lot of hair, then.

00:15:25.260 --> 00:15:26.380
It must've been tough.

00:15:27.140 --> 00:15:27.980
Forget about

00:15:27.980 --> 00:15:29.860
this tiny studio of ours.

00:15:30.580 --> 00:15:33.540
Even those big-time clients

00:15:33.660 --> 00:15:35.580
who've sailed smoothly for decades

00:15:35.580 --> 00:15:37.460
will be knocked off their feet
by a single wave,

00:15:37.460 --> 00:15:37.980
you know?

00:15:37.980 --> 00:15:39.660
Such examples are everywhere.

00:15:41.560 --> 00:15:42.420
I have to stop here.

00:15:42.420 --> 00:15:43.690
I need to visit the F&B Department.

00:15:43.700 --> 00:15:45.060
Someone complained about Rufeng Liquor.

00:15:45.060 --> 00:15:46.420
I have to help
the suppliers deal with it.

00:15:46.420 --> 00:15:47.620
Is that included
in your job scope as well?

00:15:47.820 --> 00:15:49.950
Didn't I tell you already?
It's difficult to make money nowadays.

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:53.940
I have to make sure
I provide good services

00:15:53.940 --> 00:15:55.330
to my clients
while I can still move around.

00:15:55.340 --> 00:15:57.220
I'm going to keep every penny I earn

00:15:57.220 --> 00:15:58.980
firmly in my own hands.

00:15:59.260 --> 00:15:59.940
Let me join you.

00:15:59.940 --> 00:16:01.560
- It's fine. Just resume your work.
- This is troublesome indeed.

00:16:01.570 --> 00:16:02.860
Sorry that you have
to come here personally.

00:16:02.860 --> 00:16:03.580
Mr. Ding.

00:16:03.740 --> 00:16:06.380
All those alcoholics love to cause trouble
after getting drunk.

00:16:07.220 --> 00:16:08.260
But to us,

00:16:08.260 --> 00:16:09.580
the customer is always right.

00:16:10.100 --> 00:16:11.100
Please bear with it.

00:16:11.500 --> 00:16:12.660
No problem.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:14.020
Let's discuss this in the office.

00:16:14.360 --> 00:16:16.700
By the way, Mr. Feng has used up
all the money on his card.

00:16:16.900 --> 00:16:18.540
And now, he owes us a few thousand yuan.

00:16:18.580 --> 00:16:20.420
You know this too.
Business is hard nowadays.

00:16:20.500 --> 00:16:21.580
Please tell him about it later.

00:16:21.580 --> 00:16:23.140
That's fine. I'll pay it off after this.

00:16:23.220 --> 00:16:24.260
There's no rush.

00:16:24.740 --> 00:16:25.700
It just occurred to me.

00:16:25.700 --> 00:16:26.740
That's why I told you.

00:16:26.740 --> 00:16:27.380
It'll be fine.

00:16:27.460 --> 00:16:28.860
I'll ask him to reimburse me later.

00:16:28.860 --> 00:16:30.180
Okay. Let's go, then.

00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:30.700
I'll make a move now.

00:16:30.700 --> 00:16:31.650
Okay. You guys can go ahead.

00:16:31.660 --> 00:16:32.580
Come. Over here.

00:16:35.700 --> 00:16:36.300
What?

00:16:37.340 --> 00:16:38.020
I owe them money?

00:16:39.420 --> 00:16:41.300
So, how much have you paid
on my behalf?

00:16:41.820 --> 00:16:42.780
3,500 yuan.

00:16:42.790 --> 00:16:44.620
Okay. Sorry about that.
I'll transfer the money to you now.

00:16:44.620 --> 00:16:46.220
Dad, it's fine. There's no rush.

00:16:46.220 --> 00:16:47.300
I'm so forgetful now.

00:16:49.940 --> 00:16:51.260
(Balance)

00:16:55.540 --> 00:16:56.860
What was my password again?

00:16:56.860 --> 00:16:58.220
I can't remember it.

00:16:58.220 --> 00:16:58.940
Dad, it's fine.

00:16:58.940 --> 00:17:00.160
You don't need to pay me back.

00:17:00.260 --> 00:17:01.100
Don't worry.

00:17:01.110 --> 00:17:02.020
I'll transfer it to you later.

00:17:02.020 --> 00:17:03.460
It's fine. You don't need to pay me.

00:17:08.220 --> 00:17:08.700
Lihua.

00:17:09.580 --> 00:17:10.060
Lihua?

00:17:10.660 --> 00:17:11.820
I need to tell you something.

00:17:11.940 --> 00:17:12.580
What's wrong?

00:17:13.980 --> 00:17:16.700
Transfer 3,500 yuan to Mingzhu.

00:17:16.980 --> 00:17:17.700
For what?

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:19.500
Why should I transfer the money to her?
Why aren't you doing it?

00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:20.960
I didn't bring that much money with me

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.140
when I went to their hotel last time.

00:17:22.140 --> 00:17:23.370
Mingzhu paid off
the balance on my behalf.

00:17:23.380 --> 00:17:23.900
Transfer the money to her.

00:17:23.900 --> 00:17:25.740
I'll transfer it to you
when I come back from work.

00:17:27.860 --> 00:17:29.700
You see, I forgot my password.

00:17:29.700 --> 00:17:31.140
It's all because you drink too much.

00:17:31.140 --> 00:17:32.460
You even forgot about your password.

00:17:32.460 --> 00:17:33.140
Keep on drinking,

00:17:33.140 --> 00:17:34.580
and you'll grow senile.

00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:36.860
I'll transfer the money to her later.

00:17:42.620 --> 00:17:45.460
Even those big-time clients

00:17:45.700 --> 00:17:47.460
who've sailed smoothly for decades

00:17:47.460 --> 00:17:49.420
will be knocked off their feet
by a single wave,

00:17:49.420 --> 00:17:49.940
you know?

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:51.540
Such examples are everywhere.

00:17:51.540 --> 00:17:52.340
(Usable Balance)

00:18:29.060 --> 00:18:29.820
(Jianqi,)

00:18:30.460 --> 00:18:32.620
(I'm going to secure
this house for my baby.)

00:18:33.140 --> 00:18:34.380
(Will you blame me for this?)

00:18:34.960 --> 00:18:37.180
(I'm going to do it even if
you're blaming me for it.)

00:18:37.380 --> 00:18:38.700
(It's because I'm a mother.)

00:18:45.380 --> 00:18:46.300
Are you saying

00:18:47.120 --> 00:18:49.350
that you want to transfer
the ownership of this marital house?

00:18:51.060 --> 00:18:53.620
This unit is registered
under Jianqi's name.

00:18:54.500 --> 00:18:56.060
When Jianqi left,

00:18:56.540 --> 00:18:57.660
you guys promised me

00:18:57.940 --> 00:18:59.420
that I would own this house

00:19:00.060 --> 00:19:01.620
once I gave birth to your grandchild.

00:19:02.700 --> 00:19:04.340
Back then, I didn't think much about it.

00:19:04.750 --> 00:19:06.620
But now, my belly is
growing bigger and bigger.

00:19:06.760 --> 00:19:08.860
I won't be able
to move around freely in the future.

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:11.160
Therefore, I want to transfer
the ownership of the house

00:19:11.580 --> 00:19:12.860
while I can still move around.

00:19:15.100 --> 00:19:17.100
I'm sure your parents
gave you that idea.

00:19:17.940 --> 00:19:19.340
No, it's my idea.

00:19:21.580 --> 00:19:24.060
The title deed is in Jianqi's name.

00:19:24.060 --> 00:19:27.020
It'll be troublesome
to do an ownership transfer.

00:19:27.020 --> 00:19:27.860
It's not.

00:19:28.060 --> 00:19:29.280
I've already inquired about it.

00:19:29.290 --> 00:19:30.850
I just need to get a notarized document

00:19:31.300 --> 00:19:33.940
stating that you and Dad
will relinquish the inheritance right.

00:19:37.780 --> 00:19:39.300
It's not like my parents will scam you.

00:19:39.580 --> 00:19:40.860
Why are you getting it notarized?

00:19:41.660 --> 00:19:42.420
Precisely.

00:19:43.900 --> 00:19:45.340
We're a family.

00:19:46.420 --> 00:19:49.020
We will keep our promise.

00:19:49.500 --> 00:19:50.140
Besides,

00:19:50.940 --> 00:19:52.700
the title deed is in Jianqi's name.

00:19:52.700 --> 00:19:54.260
That means the house is yours.

00:19:55.700 --> 00:19:57.540
The house isn't mine

00:19:58.180 --> 00:19:59.950
as long as the title deed
isn't in my name.

00:20:03.900 --> 00:20:06.860
But what if you get remarried?

00:20:07.380 --> 00:20:08.700
This is pre-marital property.

00:20:09.100 --> 00:20:11.340
I'm securing it for my child.

00:20:12.060 --> 00:20:13.420
Once I give birth to my child,

00:20:13.430 --> 00:20:15.060
I'll include his name in the title deed.

00:20:16.080 --> 00:20:17.780
If so, you can just add
the child's name to the title deed

00:20:17.780 --> 00:20:19.500
once he's born.

00:20:20.180 --> 00:20:21.450
Why go through all that trouble?

00:20:22.180 --> 00:20:24.180
What about my interest as his mother?

00:20:24.710 --> 00:20:27.420
Did you decide to give birth to a child
only because of the interest?

00:20:30.420 --> 00:20:32.180
I decided to have a child first.

00:20:32.820 --> 00:20:35.300
That's why I'm trying to secure
our interests here.

00:20:35.300 --> 00:20:35.900
Wait.

00:20:36.580 --> 00:20:38.940
Our family helped out
in decorating the house

00:20:38.940 --> 00:20:39.890
and the children's room.

00:20:39.900 --> 00:20:41.100
Isn't that good enough?

00:20:41.210 --> 00:20:43.100
Must you talk about
such materialistic things...

00:20:43.100 --> 00:20:44.540
Enough.

00:20:47.020 --> 00:20:49.300
We should keep our promise.

00:20:51.980 --> 00:20:54.140
Mingzhu, go and perform the procedure.

00:20:54.460 --> 00:20:56.050
We'll do our best to cooperate with you.

00:20:56.660 --> 00:20:57.500
Thank you, Dad.

00:20:59.820 --> 00:21:00.700
I'll head to work now.

00:21:05.500 --> 00:21:06.060
Let's eat.

00:21:14.860 --> 00:21:15.860
That was too hasty.

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:18.860
You told your parents-in-law that you
wanted to do an ownership transfer,

00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:20.120
and they actually agreed to it?

00:21:21.620 --> 00:21:23.940
But I offended
my mother-in-law and Meiqi again.

00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:26.140
That's fine.

00:21:26.140 --> 00:21:28.240
If you don't offend them,
you'll swallow grievances.

00:21:29.540 --> 00:21:31.020
Yesterday, I saw my father-in-law's

00:21:31.020 --> 00:21:32.180
Alipay account.

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:33.940
He only has a few hundred yuan left.

00:21:34.160 --> 00:21:36.660
I was wondering if his company
is facing some sort of trouble.

00:21:39.140 --> 00:21:40.060
It won't be that bad.

00:21:42.140 --> 00:21:43.900
Anyway, I want to help my child

00:21:44.260 --> 00:21:45.700
to hold on to everything

00:21:45.700 --> 00:21:46.820
that I can grasp in my hand.

00:21:50.980 --> 00:21:52.860
Am I being too selfish?

00:21:53.820 --> 00:21:55.140
How is this selfish?

00:21:55.160 --> 00:21:56.420
You're doing this for your child.

00:21:56.420 --> 00:21:57.580
It's not selfish at all.

00:21:57.590 --> 00:21:58.680
Besides, your parents-in-law

00:21:58.690 --> 00:22:00.220
already promised to give you the house.

00:22:00.220 --> 00:22:00.780
Am I right?

00:22:00.860 --> 00:22:02.620
It's time for them
to keep their promise.

00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:03.980
I suppose you could say that.

00:22:04.820 --> 00:22:06.260
Anyway, my mother-in-law and Meiqi

00:22:06.260 --> 00:22:07.460
were quite upset.

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:10.740
Meiqi is upset, huh?

00:22:12.260 --> 00:22:12.900
Oh no.

00:22:12.900 --> 00:22:13.620
What's wrong?

00:22:13.660 --> 00:22:15.440
Will it affect her
from being Bichen's bridesmaid?

00:22:22.180 --> 00:22:22.900
Please sign here.

00:22:23.220 --> 00:22:23.660
Okay.

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:28.300
(Real Estate Registration)

00:22:31.360 --> 00:22:31.900
Here you go.

00:22:33.980 --> 00:22:34.620
Keep it well.

00:22:35.700 --> 00:22:36.380
Is that all?

00:22:36.380 --> 00:22:36.980
Yes.

00:22:36.980 --> 00:22:37.540
Okay.

00:22:37.620 --> 00:22:39.260
(People's Republic of China
Real Estate Ownership Certificate)

00:22:39.460 --> 00:22:40.100
Here.

00:22:40.100 --> 00:22:40.980
(Shen Mingzhu)

00:22:40.980 --> 00:22:41.860
Shen Mingzhu.

00:22:44.540 --> 00:22:45.180
All done.

00:22:45.980 --> 00:22:47.380
The ownership has been transferred.

00:22:48.260 --> 00:22:49.700
Your name is in the title deed now.

00:22:50.140 --> 00:22:51.140
You can rest at ease now.

00:22:51.620 --> 00:22:52.500
Thank you, Mom.

00:22:54.620 --> 00:22:55.340
Mingzhu,

00:22:56.180 --> 00:22:59.620
we also have some conditions
that you need to fulfill.

00:22:59.620 --> 00:23:00.550
Is that okay with you?

00:23:01.420 --> 00:23:02.060
Please go ahead.

00:23:02.740 --> 00:23:03.660
First condition,

00:23:04.500 --> 00:23:06.060
you cannot take any men home.

00:23:07.660 --> 00:23:08.380
I won't.

00:23:09.260 --> 00:23:10.220
Once the child is born,

00:23:10.220 --> 00:23:12.750
you need to include the child's name
in the title deed as well.

00:23:13.940 --> 00:23:14.580
And,

00:23:14.860 --> 00:23:16.780
the child's surname must be Feng.

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:19.980
Jianqi and I have already
reached a consensus.

00:23:20.080 --> 00:23:21.780
If it's a boy,
we'll call him Feng Xiangru.

00:23:21.790 --> 00:23:23.440
If it's a girl,
we'll call her Feng Yimo.

00:23:23.960 --> 00:23:24.820
- That's pretty good.
- I like that.

00:23:24.820 --> 00:23:26.100
Their names are pretty nice.

00:23:26.100 --> 00:23:27.020
Yeah.

00:23:27.620 --> 00:23:28.220
What if...

00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:31.380
You see, this house

00:23:31.380 --> 00:23:33.420
is a cherished memory
Jianqi had left for us.

00:23:33.430 --> 00:23:34.140
You know this too.

00:23:34.140 --> 00:23:36.100
Your mother-in-law and I
only have one son.

00:23:37.060 --> 00:23:40.300
We're also willing to give the house

00:23:40.780 --> 00:23:42.060
to you and your child.

00:23:45.060 --> 00:23:46.150
I also have one condition.

00:23:47.780 --> 00:23:48.660
In the future,

00:23:48.670 --> 00:23:51.360
no matter how difficult life is,
no matter how much money you need,

00:23:51.860 --> 00:23:53.860
you mustn't use it as a mortgage.

00:23:55.380 --> 00:23:56.060
Dad, Mom,

00:23:56.460 --> 00:23:57.340
don't worry.

00:23:57.900 --> 00:23:59.940
You guys bought this house for your son.

00:24:01.040 --> 00:24:02.950
Since Jianqi wasn't
fortunate enough to live here,

00:24:03.700 --> 00:24:04.780
he's leaving it to his son.

00:24:06.360 --> 00:24:07.700
I'm just looking after it for him.

00:24:10.940 --> 00:24:12.180
Okay. Thank you.

00:24:12.900 --> 00:24:13.580
Here, take it.

00:24:14.820 --> 00:24:15.780
Thank you, Dad and Mom.

00:24:27.620 --> 00:24:28.220
Mingzhu.

00:24:28.900 --> 00:24:30.020
You're a house owner now.

00:24:30.020 --> 00:24:30.900
Mingzhu.

00:24:30.980 --> 00:24:32.280
You should give me a red packet.

00:24:33.580 --> 00:24:34.450
Stop causing trouble.

00:24:34.780 --> 00:24:35.780
You have to give me one.

00:24:35.780 --> 00:24:38.140
If not, I'll cause trouble for you
at your new house every day.

00:24:38.140 --> 00:24:39.060
Feng and his family

00:24:39.070 --> 00:24:41.020
did keep their promise.
They're quite credible.

00:24:41.740 --> 00:24:42.820
Our daughter did great.

00:24:43.260 --> 00:24:45.000
Now that she owns a house,

00:24:45.010 --> 00:24:47.980
she'll face much less financial pressure
after she gives birth to her child.

00:24:47.980 --> 00:24:48.640
Don't you agree?

