00:34:59.900 --> 00:35:01.060
May you have a child soon.

00:35:01.060 --> 00:35:01.820
Thank you so much.

00:35:01.820 --> 00:35:03.940
So, where's the toilet?

00:35:04.460 --> 00:35:05.340
It's over there.

00:35:05.350 --> 00:35:06.540
- I need to use the toilet.
- Mom, I'll join you.

00:35:06.540 --> 00:35:07.500
I'll be fine. You can stay here.

00:35:07.500 --> 00:35:08.180
I'll be back in a second.

00:35:08.180 --> 00:35:09.380
I drank too much water just now.

00:35:09.380 --> 00:35:10.340
I need to take a leak.

00:35:10.780 --> 00:35:11.700
Take care.

00:35:13.860 --> 00:35:14.820
Mingzhu, you're here.

00:35:15.300 --> 00:35:16.020
Zhixia.

00:35:16.020 --> 00:35:16.860
Mingzhu.

00:35:17.540 --> 00:35:18.340
You're so beautiful.

00:35:19.180 --> 00:35:19.860
Mr. Shen.

00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:22.260
We're truly honored by your presence.

00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:23.620
Didn't Mrs. Shen come as well?

00:35:23.620 --> 00:35:24.420
She's here.

00:35:24.420 --> 00:35:25.460
She went to the toilet.

00:35:25.460 --> 00:35:26.490
Is your younger brother
in the toilet too?

00:35:26.500 --> 00:35:27.100
No.

00:35:27.100 --> 00:35:28.950
He's studying at home
to prepare for the NCEE.

00:35:28.980 --> 00:35:30.300
- Mingzhu.
- That's good to hear.

00:35:30.300 --> 00:35:32.180
How are you doing?

00:35:32.180 --> 00:35:33.060
I'm doing great.

00:35:33.060 --> 00:35:34.220
It's just that my child
is growing rapidly.

00:35:34.220 --> 00:35:35.140
Isn't that great? Look at me.

00:35:35.140 --> 00:35:36.140
Yeah.

00:35:37.100 --> 00:35:37.700
Oh yeah.

00:35:37.700 --> 00:35:39.020
Photographer, please help us

00:35:39.100 --> 00:35:40.700
take a family picture.

00:35:40.760 --> 00:35:41.860
- Yeah.
- I'll go and look for Mom.

00:35:41.860 --> 00:35:43.620
Mr. Shen, come and join us.

00:35:43.620 --> 00:35:44.860
No. I'll go and look for her.

00:35:44.860 --> 00:35:45.260
You?

00:35:45.260 --> 00:35:46.130
Take the family picture.

00:35:46.140 --> 00:35:46.580
Let's take one first.

00:35:46.580 --> 00:35:47.220
You guys can go ahead.

00:35:47.220 --> 00:35:48.460
Alright. We'll take one first.

00:35:48.460 --> 00:35:49.460
Okay. Come.

00:35:49.460 --> 00:35:51.020
Okay. Come here, dear.

00:35:51.020 --> 00:35:52.460
Look at me.

00:35:53.460 --> 00:35:54.180
Look at me.

00:35:54.180 --> 00:35:55.580
Three, two, one.

00:35:55.580 --> 00:35:56.140
Cheese.

00:35:56.460 --> 00:35:57.300
I'm the only one doing it.

00:35:57.300 --> 00:35:57.860
Come on, let's do it.

00:35:57.860 --> 00:35:59.180
Okay.

00:35:59.180 --> 00:36:00.060
Let's take one more. Smile.

00:36:00.060 --> 00:36:01.900
It's a family picture. Three, two, one.

00:36:01.900 --> 00:36:03.940
- Cheese!
- Cheese!

00:36:04.380 --> 00:36:05.100
Alright.

00:36:05.580 --> 00:36:06.100
Okay.

00:36:06.100 --> 00:36:06.660
Hey.

00:36:06.660 --> 00:36:06.980
Mom.

00:36:06.980 --> 00:36:07.900
That doesn't count.

00:36:07.900 --> 00:36:09.420
Mom, let's take a family picture.

00:36:09.420 --> 00:36:10.180
Yeah.

00:36:10.180 --> 00:36:11.820
They're taking a family picture.

00:36:11.900 --> 00:36:12.580
Yeah.

00:36:12.580 --> 00:36:14.100
We aren't a family.
Why are we joining them?

00:36:14.100 --> 00:36:14.860
Mrs. Shen.

00:36:15.260 --> 00:36:17.300
Join us for a family picture.

00:36:17.940 --> 00:36:18.900
It's okay.

00:36:18.900 --> 00:36:19.850
The auspicious hour is nearing.

00:36:19.860 --> 00:36:21.820
Friends and family,
please take your seats.

00:36:21.820 --> 00:36:22.220
Yeah.

00:36:22.220 --> 00:36:23.860
It's almost time.
We should proceed first.

00:36:23.870 --> 00:36:24.900
We can talk about the photo later.

00:36:24.900 --> 00:36:25.700
Let's observe the ceremony first.

00:36:25.700 --> 00:36:26.380
Was she upset?

00:36:26.380 --> 00:36:26.700
No.

00:36:26.900 --> 00:36:28.580
We reserved the VIP seats for you all.

00:36:28.580 --> 00:36:30.180
Please take your seats.

00:36:30.300 --> 00:36:32.140
Come. Please take your seats.

00:36:38.560 --> 00:36:40.550
The bride's father is
holding his daughter's hands,

00:36:41.060 --> 00:36:43.300
from her first day of school
to her wedding day...

00:36:51.700 --> 00:36:53.100
(Just a few months ago,)

00:36:53.820 --> 00:36:56.020
(I've imagined this scene
countless times.)

00:36:56.740 --> 00:36:59.100
(I discussed
how I should walk the aisle)

00:36:59.620 --> 00:37:01.980
(with my father
on my wedding day countless times.)

00:37:01.990 --> 00:37:03.100
(I pondered how to smile)

00:37:03.180 --> 00:37:05.260
(or how I should extend my arm
to my future husband.)

00:37:05.740 --> 00:37:06.700
(But now,)

00:37:07.420 --> 00:37:08.940
(my husband is no longer around.)

00:37:22.740 --> 00:37:25.020
Let's take a breather outside.

00:37:25.500 --> 00:37:26.340
Mom, I'm fine.

00:37:26.620 --> 00:37:28.020
I'm just touched

00:37:28.020 --> 00:37:29.300
that they're getting married.

00:37:29.860 --> 00:37:30.700
I'm fine.

00:37:31.620 --> 00:37:32.260
Look.

00:37:32.620 --> 00:37:33.180
Groom,

00:37:33.460 --> 00:37:35.580
you may come and embrace happiness now.

00:37:43.060 --> 00:37:45.980
I know that the bride's father

00:37:46.140 --> 00:37:47.860
must be reluctant to part with her.

00:37:48.180 --> 00:37:49.260
But at this moment,

00:37:49.260 --> 00:37:51.500
you still have
a sacred mission to complete.

00:37:51.760 --> 00:37:53.460
Please give
your precious daughter, Bichen,

00:37:53.460 --> 00:37:55.380
into the care of her groom,
Mr. Xu Zhidong,

00:37:55.900 --> 00:37:57.980
to complete the passing
and continuation of love.

00:38:14.180 --> 00:38:15.620
Bride's father, please open your arms

00:38:16.060 --> 00:38:17.380
and embrace the newlywed.

00:38:34.060 --> 00:38:35.020
Sorry about this.

00:38:35.620 --> 00:38:36.420
Host,

00:38:36.740 --> 00:38:38.380
actually, it's not time

00:38:38.380 --> 00:38:40.020
for my speech yet.

00:38:41.140 --> 00:38:43.220
You see, I already prepared a script

00:38:43.220 --> 00:38:44.180
for my speech.

00:38:44.820 --> 00:38:45.500
But now,

00:38:46.020 --> 00:38:47.820
I'm suddenly inspired.

00:38:48.300 --> 00:38:51.020
I wish to say something
to everyone here.

00:38:55.060 --> 00:38:57.180
The pictures of us

00:38:57.180 --> 00:38:58.660
on the screen

00:38:59.380 --> 00:39:01.540
were all happy and joyous moments.

00:39:02.540 --> 00:39:04.020
But that isn't all.

00:39:05.540 --> 00:39:07.780
We do have misunderstandings, conflicts,

00:39:08.500 --> 00:39:10.260
and arguments too.

00:39:12.100 --> 00:39:13.580
But just like what everyone says,

00:39:14.360 --> 00:39:16.220
it's precisely
because of these disappointments

00:39:16.220 --> 00:39:17.820
and these moments of happiness

00:39:18.380 --> 00:39:20.140
that we become whole.

00:39:21.300 --> 00:39:22.540
With these disappointments,

00:39:23.380 --> 00:39:25.280
the moments of happiness
become extra precious.

00:39:25.540 --> 00:39:26.820
With these disappointments,

00:39:27.300 --> 00:39:28.820
Chen and I were able to

00:39:29.420 --> 00:39:31.340
understand and trust each other more.

00:39:33.620 --> 00:39:35.540
With these disappointments,

00:39:36.540 --> 00:39:40.340
I was truly able
to understand the meaning of home.

00:39:43.780 --> 00:39:46.940
Though great kindness
need not be thanked,

00:39:50.140 --> 00:39:52.020
Dad, Mom,

00:39:54.580 --> 00:39:55.380
and Zhixia,

00:39:57.340 --> 00:39:58.740
thank you for your love.

00:40:00.940 --> 00:40:03.140
I will use the rest of my life
to repay your kindness.

00:40:04.780 --> 00:40:05.500
Thank you.

00:40:18.780 --> 00:40:21.180
From today onward, Chen and I

00:40:21.180 --> 00:40:22.660
will also establish our own family.

00:40:23.260 --> 00:40:24.780
I have something to tell Chen.

00:40:27.500 --> 00:40:28.220
Chen,

00:40:29.380 --> 00:40:30.820
you have to be mentally prepared.

00:40:31.660 --> 00:40:33.340
Today might be the most wonderful day

00:40:33.340 --> 00:40:34.780
of your life.

00:40:35.180 --> 00:40:37.340
After this, you will face
a ten-month pregnancy.

00:40:37.520 --> 00:40:39.950
You will give birth to our children,
and you have to raise them.

00:40:39.980 --> 00:40:41.020
You will gain weight,

00:40:41.020 --> 00:40:42.140
you will get stretch marks,

00:40:42.140 --> 00:40:44.750
and you will be so busy that
you have no time to doll yourself up.

00:40:46.020 --> 00:40:48.020
No. What I'm trying to say is

00:40:48.020 --> 00:40:50.140
that you're always be beautiful to me!

00:40:52.180 --> 00:40:53.260
I wish to say this to you.

00:40:54.660 --> 00:40:56.380
Thank you so much
for everything you did.

00:40:59.700 --> 00:41:03.460
Today,
I will announce this to the world!

00:41:04.020 --> 00:41:05.020
Yuan Bichen,

00:41:05.300 --> 00:41:06.540
I love you!

00:41:06.900 --> 00:41:08.860
Excellent!

00:41:09.860 --> 00:41:10.340
Excellent!

00:41:23.000 --> 00:41:24.580
There's one more person I need to thank.

00:41:25.500 --> 00:41:26.540
Without her,

00:41:27.340 --> 00:41:29.060
our child wouldn't have survived.

00:41:29.380 --> 00:41:31.140
And, we wouldn't be standing here.

00:41:31.820 --> 00:41:33.340
I need to thank my second sister,

00:41:34.780 --> 00:41:35.420
Shen Mingzhu.

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:37.620
You didn't need to.

00:41:38.620 --> 00:41:39.260
Mingzhu,

00:41:39.360 --> 00:41:41.660
no matter if you acknowledge me
as your brother or not,

00:41:41.700 --> 00:41:43.020
to me,

00:41:43.020 --> 00:41:44.500
we are twins,

00:41:44.500 --> 00:41:45.860
who are bound by blood.

00:41:46.780 --> 00:41:47.740
Please come on stage

00:41:47.740 --> 00:41:49.100
and be our officiant.

00:41:49.420 --> 00:41:50.540
Please give us a speech.

00:41:50.900 --> 00:41:52.060
What's going on?

00:41:52.660 --> 00:41:53.700
What did he mean by that?

00:41:53.940 --> 00:41:55.820
I thought they said
that they would drop the matter.

00:41:56.060 --> 00:41:59.060
It's obvious that they're trying
to acknowledge you through this wedding.

00:42:01.060 --> 00:42:03.260
The groom's speech was truly touching.

00:42:04.060 --> 00:42:06.300
And, Mingzhu
is her parents' precious daughter.

00:42:06.300 --> 00:42:08.940
She's also the guiding pearl
for our newlywed couple.

00:42:09.620 --> 00:42:11.180
Since she's very important,

00:42:11.180 --> 00:42:13.530
and she wants to give her blessings
to the newlywed couple,

00:42:13.540 --> 00:42:14.100
here,

00:42:14.100 --> 00:42:16.420
I would like to make a request.

00:42:16.780 --> 00:42:17.700
Everyone knows

00:42:17.700 --> 00:42:19.580
that Mingzhu is an excellent pianist.

00:42:19.780 --> 00:42:21.220
Action speaks louder than words.

00:42:21.300 --> 00:42:23.340
Next, let us give a big hand

00:42:23.340 --> 00:42:24.900
to Mrs. Shen Mingzhu.

00:42:24.900 --> 00:42:26.020
Please play a song for us,

00:42:26.020 --> 00:42:26.660
okay?

00:42:27.900 --> 00:42:29.500
Excellent!

00:42:33.520 --> 00:42:34.540
Why are you sitting down?

00:42:34.540 --> 00:42:35.460
What did I tell you?

00:42:35.460 --> 00:42:36.420
We shouldn't have come here
in the first place!

00:42:36.420 --> 00:42:38.500
They're in the middle of their wedding.

00:42:38.500 --> 00:42:39.100
For this moment...

00:42:39.100 --> 00:42:40.700
But he did it on purpose!

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:56.950
The world is noisy

00:42:57.550 --> 00:42:59.930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

00:43:01.350 --> 00:43:03.230
Once I didnt know what to do

00:43:03.230 --> 00:43:05.310
What to hold quietly

00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:08.260
Like a silent care

00:43:10.120 --> 00:43:12.530
Seasons pass by

00:43:12.530 --> 00:43:15.390
Time ticks away

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:17.790
Seems like I understand a little

00:43:17.790 --> 00:43:19.570
And also let go of some things

00:43:19.570 --> 00:43:24.290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:27.780
A long letter is written down

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.410
Gently spreading love

00:43:31.610 --> 00:43:35.600
To all the forks in fate

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:41.230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved